description:
We love Wednesday as much as, or maybe even more so than the next person. We built Wednesday Coin as an arbitrary method of celebrating Wednesdays!

Other days just don't compare to Wednesdays. Trade on Wednesdays and spent the rest of your week with your friends or family, relaxing and having fun! No need to constantly check the price because even if the price is high, if it is not Wednesday you can't sell.
name: Wednesday Coin
